  Locus:
    Page: 289
    Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Life is a gift from God
---
It is given to the world to learn one great divine lesson, the lesson of
absolute selflessness. The saints, sages and saviors of all time are they
who have submitted themselves to this task, and have learned and lived it.
